endations: failed to get recommended product info (#PHOTO456): rpc error: code = Canceled desc = context canceled\"\",\"\"http.req.id\"\":\"\"6459d3e6-0975-49bc-b57a-a78febe1e2e2\"\",\"\"http.req.method\"\":\"\"GET\"\",\"\"http.req.path\"\":\"\"/cart\"\",\"\"message\"\":\"\"request error\"\",\"\"session\"\":\"\"b84c0ed5-3a59-45b9-9a38-a7cfe7c282da\"\",\"\"severity\"\":\"\"error\"\",\"\"timestamp\"\":\"\"2025-06-14T03:24:21.33679332Z\"\"}\",出现次数:1\n", "unique_entities": {"pod_name": ["frontend-2", "frontend-1", "frontend-0"], "service_name": ["frontend"], "node_name": ["aiops-k8s-04", "aiops-k8s-07", "aiops-k8s-03"]}, "matched_anomaly": "A fault was detected from 2025-06-14T03:10:24Z to 2025-06-14T03:28:24Z. Please analyze its root cause.", "time_range": "2025-06-14 03:10:24+00:00 to 2025-06-14 03:28:24+00:00"}, "log_data_collected": true, "log_analysis_findings": "基于对故障时间段内日志数据的分析，我已完成初始扫描。以下是分析结果：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"context canceled\", \"rpc error\", \"code = Canceled\", \"failed to get product recommendations\", \"could not retrieve product\", \"could not retrieve products\", \"could not retrieve currencies\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"RPC调用超时导致context canceled错误，影响产品信息获取\",\n      \"evidence\": \"could not retrieve product: rpc error: code = Canceled desc = context canceled\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"currencyservice\", \n      \"reason\": \"RPC调用超时导致context canceled错误，影响货币信息获取\",\n      \"evidence\": \"could not retrieve currencies: rpc error: code = Canceled desc = context canceled\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"recommendationservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"RPC调用超时导致context canceled错误，影响产品推荐功能\",\n      \"evidence\": \"failed to get product recommendations: failed to get recommended product info (#XXX): rpc error: code = Canceled desc = context canceled\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"前端服务报告RPC调用超时，但可能是下游服务问题\",\n      \"evidence\": \"多个frontend实例报告相同的RPC调用超时错误模式\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n### 关键发现：\n1. **统一的错误模式**: 所有错误都表现为 `rpc error: code = Canceled desc = context canceled`，表明RPC调用超时\n2. **影响范围**: 主要影响产品目录、货币服务和推荐服务三个下游服务\n3. **时间分布**: 错误集中在03:11-03:14时间段，持续约3分钟\n4. **服务模式**: frontend作为调用方，多个下游服务同时出现响应超时\n\n**建议下一步**: 需要获取下游服务(productcatalogservice, currencyservice, recommendationservice)的日志，以确定是网络问题、资源瓶颈还是服务本身故障。", "trace_analysis_findings": "基于采集到的链路追踪数据，我已经完成了初始扫描阶段的分析。以下是详细的发现：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"error_ratio\",\n    \"frontend->productcatalogservice\",\n    \"frontend->frontend\",\n    \"checkoutservice->paymentservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->shippingservice\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend服务\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend对ProductCatalogService的调用延迟异常激增：GetProduct操作从正常11.3秒激增至56.9秒（延迟倍数5,000倍），ListProducts操作从正常2秒激增至59秒（延迟倍数29,500倍）\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice服务\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"productcatalogservice自身处理延迟相对稳定（GetProduct从10秒增至12-13秒），但frontend调用productcatalogservice时出现严重延迟，表明网络或连接层问题\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice服务\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"checkoutservice的PlaceOrder操作延迟从正常143.5秒增至387.7秒，PaymentService和ShippingService调用延迟分别从12.8秒增至80.5秒、12.5秒增至78.8秒\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"前端到产品目录服务链路\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"大量context canceled错误（GetProduct: 124-143次，ListProducts: 13-31次）和transport is closing错误，表明连接不稳定或超时\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"前端HTTP接口\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"前端HTTP接口出现大量500错误（每个frontend实例约155-165次），表明服务整体不可用\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**关键发现总结：**\n\n1. **严重延迟问题**：frontend服务调用productcatalogservice时出现极端延迟，延迟倍数达到5,000-29,500倍\n2. **连接稳定性问题**：大量context canceled和transport is closing错误表明网络连接不稳定\n3. **级联影响**：checkoutservice也受到影响，但程度相对较轻\n4. **根因指向**：问题主要出现在frontend到productcatalogservice的调用链路，可能是网络问题或productcatalogservice连接池问题", "metric_analysis_findings": "基于获取到的指标数据，我现在进行初始扫描分析。从异常指标数据来看，主要发现了服务级别的错误率异常。\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"client_error_ratio\", \"error_ratio\", \"server_error_ratio\", \"pod_cpu_usage\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"多个frontend实例出现server_error_ratio和error_ratio显著升高\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend-0: server_error_ratio从0.0升至32.2(median), error_ratio从0.0升至32.2; frontend-1: server_error_ratio从0.0升至35.54, error_ratio从0.0升至35.54; frontend-2: server_error_ratio从0.0升至33.9, error_ratio从0.0升至33.9\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"所有shippingservice实例的client_error_ratio和error_ratio异常升高\",\n      \"evidence\": \"shippingservice-0: client_error_ratio从0.0升至58.3, error_ratio从0.0升至58.3; shippingservice-1: client_error_ratio从0.0升至61.7, error_ratio从0.0升至61.7; shippingservice-2: client_error_ratio从0.0升至51.15, error_ratio从0.0升至51.15\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"cartservice实例的client_error_ratio和error_ratio异常升高\",\n      \"evidence\": \"cartservice-0: client_error_ratio从0.0升至45.59, error_ratio从0.0升至45.59; cartservice-1: client_error_ratio从0.0升至45.59, error_ratio从0.0升至45.59; cartservice-2: client_error_ratio从0.0升至24.2, error_ratio从0.0升至24.2\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"productcatalogservice实例的client_error_ratio和error_ratio异常升高\",\n      \"evidence\": \"productcatalogservice-1: client_error_ratio从0.0升至16.82, error_ratio从0.0升至16.82; productcatalogservice-2: client_error_ratio从0.0升至42.55, error_ratio从0.0升至42.55\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"checkoutservice实例的client_error_ratio和error_ratio异常升高\",\n      \"evidence\": \"checkoutservice-0: client_error_ratio从0.0升至18.83, error_ratio从0.0升至18.83; checkoutservice-2: client_error_ratio从0.0升至20.34, error_ratio从0.0升至20.34\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"pod_cpu_usage异常下降，从0.04降至0.0\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend-0的pod_cpu_usage从正常中位数0.04降至故障期间0.0，下降率2.0\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"pod_cpu_usage异常下降，从0.04降至0.0\",\n      \"evidence\": \"productcatalogservice-0的pod_cpu_usage从正常中位数0.04降至故障期间0.0，下降率2.0\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```"}
